  "attachmentHtml": "\n<p><strong>PC Number: </strong>2006-0693<br></p><p><strong>Date: </strong>2006-06-27</p><hr><p>    </p><div>  <p style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\">&nbsp;</p>  <p style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\">&nbsp;</p>  </div>  <br clear=\"all\" style=\"page-break-before:auto\">   <div>  <p style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:4.0in;line-height: 150%\">&nbsp;</p>  <p style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:4.0in;line-height: 150%\">&nbsp;</p>  <p style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\">&nbsp;</p>  <p style=\"line-height:150%\">&nbsp;</p>  <p style=\"line-height:150%\">&nbsp;</p>  <p class=\"MsoBodyTextIndent\">Attendu que l'honorable Thomas P. Callon, juge de la Cour de justice de l’Ontario (Division générale), a atteint l'âge de soixante‑quinze ans le 6 mars 1993, a pris sa retraite le même jour et qu'une pension de </p>  <p class=\"MsoBodyTextIndent\" style=\"text-indent:0in\">103 866,66 $ lui a été accordée par le décret C.P. 1993-207 du 4 février 1993;</p>  <p style=\"line-height:150%\">&nbsp;</p>  <p style=\"text-indent:1.0in;line-height:150%\">Attendu que ledit Thomas P. Callon est décédé le 1er mai 2006 et que sa veuve, Tamera Callon, lui survit,</p>  <p style=\"line-height:150%\">&nbsp;</p>  <p style=\"text-indent:1.0in;line-height:150%\">À ces causes, sur recommandation du ministre de la Justice et en vertu de l'article 44 de la <em>Loi sur les juges</em>, Son Excellence la Gouverneure générale en conseil accorde une pension viagère de 51 933,33 $ à Tamera Callon, à compter du 2 mai 2006.</p>  <p style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\">&nbsp;</p>  </div>  <br clear=\"all\" style=\"page-break-before:always\">   <div class=\"Section3\">  <p style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\">&nbsp;</p>  <p style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\">&nbsp;</p>  </div>  <br clear=\"all\" style=\"page-break-before:auto\">   <div class=\"Section4\">  <p style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:4.0in;line-height: 150%\">&nbsp;</p>  <p style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\">&nbsp;</p>  <p style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\">&nbsp;</p>  <p style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\">&nbsp;</p>  <p style=\"line-height:150%\">&nbsp;</p>  <p style=\"line-height:150%\">&nbsp;</p>  <p class=\"MsoBodyTextIndent\">Whereas the Honourable Thomas P. Callon, a Judge of the Ontario Court of Justice (General Division), attained the age of seventy‑five years on March 6, 1993, retired on that date and was granted an annuity of $103,866.66 by Order in Council P.C. 1993-207 dated February 4, 1993;</p>  <p style=\"line-height:150%\">&nbsp;</p>  <p style=\"text-indent:1.0in;line-height:150%\">And whereas the aforementioned Thomas P. Callon died on May 1, 2006 and is survived by a widow, Tamera Callon;</p>  <p style=\"line-height:150%\">&nbsp;</p>  <p style=\"text-indent:1.0in;line-height:150%\">Therefore, Her Excellency the Governor General in Council, on the recommendation of the Minister of Justice, pursuant to section 44 of the <em>Judges Act</em>, hereby grants an annuity of $51,933.33 to Tamera Callon, effective May 2, 2006, and to continue thenceforth during her life.</p>  <p style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:150%\">&nbsp;</p>  </div>  <br clear=\"all\" style=\"page-break-before:auto\">   <div class=\"Section5\">  <p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>  <p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>  <p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>  </div>  <strong><br clear=\"all\" style=\"page-break-before:auto\"> </strong>  <div class=\"Section6\">  <p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>  <p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>  <p style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>  <p style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>  <p style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>  </div>  <strong><br clear=\"all\" style=\"page-break-before:auto\"> </strong>  <div class=\"Section7\">  <p><strong><u>&nbsp;</u></strong></p>  <p><strong><u>&nbsp;</u></strong></p>  </div>  <strong><u><br clear=\"all\" style=\"page-break-before:auto\"> </u></strong>  <div class=\"Section8\">  <p><strong><u>&nbsp;</u></strong></p>  <p><strong><u>&nbsp;</u></strong></p>  <p><strong><u>&nbsp;</u></strong></p>  <p><strong><u>&nbsp;</u></strong></p>  <p><strong><u>&nbsp;</u></strong></p>  <p><strong><u>&nbsp;</u></strong></p>  <p><strong><u>&nbsp;</u></strong></p>  <p><strong><u>&nbsp;</u></strong></p>  </div>    \n<p></p><form method=\"post\" action=\"index.php\"><input type=\"submit\" value=\"Back to Form\" class=\"btn btn-primary\" name=\"return\"></form>\t\t\n        <!-- end main content -->\n        <div id=\"def-preFooter\">\n       \t\t<!-- Write closure fall-back static file -->\n             <!--Response.Write readFile(\"StaticFallbackFiles/gcweb/preFooter-\" & $lang & \".html\") -->\n        </div>\n\t\t<!-- Write closure template -->\n        <script type=\"text/javascript\">\n            var defPreFooter = document.getElementById(\"def-preFooter\");\n            defPreFooter.outerHTML = wet.builder.preFooter({\n                cdnEnv: \"prod\",\n                dateModified: \"2022-07-11\",\n                showPostContent: true\n            });\n        </script>\n    "
